Package com.ece.superkids.ui.user.panels

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NewGamePanel
    Creates new form NewGamePanel This creates a level selection screen panel The available levels depend on whether this a new game or continuing on a game.
    OptionPanel
    Creates new form OptionPanel containing settings to change the sound and view report cards.
    QuestionPanel
    Creates a QuestionPanel form with the specified question
    ScoreScreenPanel
    Creates new form ScoreScreenPanel Number of stars are based on scoring for that category Achievement unlocks are based on total score of the user.
    ScoresHistoryPanel
    Creates new form ScoresHistoryPanel The Scores History panel display information about how well the user performed for each level.
    SoundPanel
    Creates new form SoundPanel This panel controls the background music.
    StarPanel
    Creates new form StarPanel Shows a star.
    StartScreenPanel
    Creates new form StartScreenPanel This is main screen when the child user logs in.
    SubjectSelectionPanel
    Creates new form SubjectSelectionPanel User chooses which level of difficulty they want to play Each level has different categories.
    UserSelectionPanel
    Creates new form UserSelectionPanel This is the login screen for the child.
